questions.quote: This may surprise you, but re-hiring fired employees, is not my main job.
Oh, I'm so glad you called. I feel like it's always me calling you. So, what's up? Is everything okay with Phoebe?
Get him! GET HIM! Get him! Get- YESSS! Not laughing now, are ya pal!
I know! Now look, there's only one problem though. There's only room for one, so I guess one of you will have to stay at Joey's.
Ah, it's not so much you, you were fat, you had your own problems. But you? What a bitch!
No. So what. So what if we get beaten up, maybe that's just something every man has to go through once in his life. Ya know, like a, like a right of passage or somethin'.
Oh, I wish there was a job where I could wear this all the time. Maybe someday, there will be.
Oh, it's a tattoo! That's weird, Phoebe doesn't... Wait that's Ursula! That's not Phoebe that is Ursula!
Tell my son that I love him. Excellent! Well, okay, I gotta have some more fun!
No-no-no, I'm serious. You don't smell it? Something's on fire.
